cells.data: -- nubBy :: (a -> a -> Bool) -> [a] -> [a]on nubBy(f, xs)	set g to mReturn(f)'s |λ|		script notEq		property fEq : g		on |λ|(a)			script				on |λ|(b)					not fEq(a, b)				end |λ|			end script		end |λ|	end script		script go		on |λ|(xs)			if (length of xs) > 1 then				set x to item 1 of xs				{x} & go's |λ|(filter(notEq's |λ|(x), items 2 thru -1 of xs))			else				xs			end if		end |λ|	end script		go's |λ|(xs)end nubBy
